import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import './registerServiceWorker'
import  jQuery from 'jquery'
window.$ = window.jQuery = jQuery
import  'popper.js'
import  'bootstrap'
import './assets/app.scss'


Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  router,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
